      "text": "Wehl notifke ta KUNGA\nWahrds us man/ un fazzija:"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu Zilweka Behrns/ fak-\net us to: Tu eſſi weena Sem-\nme/ ko ne warr jchihſtihſt/ kas\nne aplihſt tai Dufmibas Deena."
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Weena Saderreſchana irr\nſtarp winnas Prawecfcheem\nwinnas Widdû/ itt ka ruhzams\nLauna/ kad tas kahdu Laupiju-\nmu laupa/ tee chd tahs Dweh-\nfeles/ tee atxem to Mantu un\ndahrgas Leetas nohſt/ tee darra\ndauds Atraitnu winnas Widdsi."
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Winnaſ Preesteri padar-\nra mannai Bauſlibat Warras-\nDarbu/ un ſagahna mannas\nſwehtas Leetas/ ſtarp twehtu un\nnesivehtu ne darra tee Starpi-\nbu/ nedſ mahza to Starpihu\nſtarp jchihſtu un neschihſtu/tee\naptlepj ſawas Azzis no man-\nnahm Swehdeenahm/ un es toh-\npu no teem ſagahnihts."
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Winnaſ Leel-Kungi irr\nwinnaſ Widdû ka Wilki/ kas\nweenu Laupijumu laupa/ Affini\niſteij/ Dwehfeles nomaita/tapehz\nka tee Negaufibu dsenn."
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winnaſ Brawecfcht\napmett tohs ar nelihpamu Skal-\nti/ un redſ aplamas Parahdi-\nſchanas/ un fluddina teem Mel.\nlub/ un falca: Ta ſakka tas\nKUNGS KUNGS: Kur tomehr\ntas KUNGS ne irr runnajs."
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Lee Eauvis rahs Se-\nmes dsenn Warras-Darbu/\nlaupa drohſchi/ ir to Nabba-\nnu Behdigu tee plehſch/ un\nSwefchineeku tee nospaida\nTeesas."
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es tad mekleju wee\nWihru no teem/ kas to Seb-\natkat fataiſitu/ un mannā Pre-\nicha prett to Schkirbu ſtahwe-\npreeſich tahs Semmes/ ka es\nne maitatu/ bet es ne atrad-\nneweenu."
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz efimu es fa-\nBahrſibu pahr teem iſlebj-\nzaur to Ugguni mannas Apſt-\nichanas efimu es teem Gallud-\nrijs/ es efimu winno Zeltu te-\nus fawu Galwu mettis/ fa-\ntas KUNGS KUNGS."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ehl notifke ta KUN-\nWahrds us man /\nfazzija:"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu Zilweka Behrns/ d-\nSeewas bija weenas Mah-\nMeitas/"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tahs dsinne Manzibu\ngivtes Semmē/ ſawā Jaun-\ndsinne tahs Manzibu/ tur ta-\nwinnu Kruhtis aptamptas/\ntahs Puppas winnu Jumi-\nwibas aptanſtitas."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tai leelafat bija �-\nWah"
    }
